Package database.keeper Description

This package holds the I/O classes for Redis cache only. StateKeeper manipulates the user state. HistKeeper stores the user meal history. LogKeeper stores the user interaction logs. MenuKeeper stores the original user menu input. SerializeKeeper is a inner base class which store an arbitrary JSONObject into the redis database.
